author: Associated Press
title: New York City Coronavirus Deaths Top 1,000 as Officials Warn Worst Is Yet to Come
description: The N.Y.C. Health Department reported Tuesday that nearly 1,100 people have died of COVID-19 in the city, with over 1,500 deaths across the state.
content:
(NEW YORK) — Deaths from the coronavirus topped 1,000 in New York City as officials warned that the worst of the virus’ toll is yet to come.
